snippet.title: Lightwood Laminate | FULL VERSION | (OKAY – 13ounce & Internet Historian remix)
snippet.description:
Created by The Pilot: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1IBCbt9eb0-1hts6AOvQsg

Here it is, the FULL VERSION of Lightwood Laminate (OKAY – 13ounce & Internet Historian remix)! After the immense response, The Pilot got on the original Lightwood Laminate remix and decided to make a full version of  Lightwood Laminate. Needless to say, it still slaps! 

Still just OKAY – 13ounce and remixed it with the one and only Internet Historian saying lightwood laminate from the video 'The Fall of 76'. NGL it kinda bounces tho.
